{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_01","textHome":"我是魔法报告界的明星，小圆前辈哦。@你见到了魔法纪录中的我了吗？@不过彩羽没能抽到我，伤心地嚎啕大哭呢。@不是这个世界的彩羽而是那个世界的……@一会这边一会那边真是好麻烦。@总之，我虽然少了一颗星，@但我也是魔法报告世界的明星——小圆前辈！@请多指教。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":210200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_18","textHome":"和馒头加农炮进行沟通可是很难的哟。@情绪兴奋的时候，不自觉地就会发射炮弹，@别忘了躲一下哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":210200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":101}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_19","textHome":"也就是说，我踢人的力量增强了？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":210200,"motion":101}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_20","textHome":"已经有两个我被实装了哦。"}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_21","textHome":"其他的我都是四星，@所以从三星进化成四星是属于我的特权。@很开心哟？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_22","textHome":"普通的我，穿着盛装的我，@加上已经实装了的魔法报告的我，@差不多该组一个只有我的队伍了吧。@当然，助战借来的，也是魔法报告的我对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_00_23","textHome":"我下次再实装又是什么时候呢？@这次的我，实装了馒头加农炮和馒头巨蟹，@让我看上去就很强……@真期待下次的我是什么样的啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":210200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":210200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp.json","id":210200,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":210251,"motion":102,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_51_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":210251,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":210251,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":210251}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":210251,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2102_51_25"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_053.exp.json","id":210251,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id